<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover, user-scalable=yes">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#C8AD8B">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent">
    <title>售後服務追蹤＋奶茶小遊戲 | 網頁版</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
        }

        body {
            background: #F7EFE1;
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', 'Inter', 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            padding: 20px 16px 40px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* 卡片樣式 - 奶茶色系 */
        .card {
            background: #FFFBF5;
            border-radius: 32px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(139, 89, 57, 0.08);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            border: 1px solid #EDDFC7;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 1.9rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
            color: #5E3A2C;
        }

        h1 span {
            background: #F1E5D2;
            padding: 6px 10px;
            border-radius: 60px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .sub {
            color: #9B7B5C;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            border-left: 3px solid #D9B48B;
            padding-left: 12px;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #D9B48B;
            padding-left: 12px;
            color: #5E3A2C;
        }

        .flex-row {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 0.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        }

        .form-group {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 140px;
        }

        label {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #A27B5C;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        input, select, button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 14px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1.5px solid #EADBC5;
            background: #FFFFFF;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: 0.2s;
            outline: none;
            font-family: inherit;
            color: #4B3621;
        }

        input:focus, select:focus {
            border-color: #C8AD8B;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(200, 173, 139, 0.25);
        }

        button {
            background: #D9B48B;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 600;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        button:active {
            transform: scale(0.97);
            background: #C8A27A;
        }

        .btn-outline {
            background: #F4EDE2;
            color: #8B5A3C;
            border: 1px solid #E2D1BA;
        }

        .btn-outline:active {
            background: #E8DCCB;
        }

        .search-bar {
            background: #FFF8F0;
            border-radius: 60px;
            padding: 4px 16px 4px 20px;
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            border: 1px solid #EDDFC7;
        }
        .search-bar input {
            border: none;
            background: transparent;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }
        .search-bar input:focus {
            box-shadow: none;
        }
        .search-bar button {
            width: auto;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 40px;
        }

        /* 紀錄卡片 */
        .record-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
        }
        .record-item {
            background: #FFFCF8;
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            border: 1px solid #EFE2D2;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
            transition: 0.1s;
        }
        .record-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .customer-name {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            color: #5E3A2C;
        }
        .service-badge {
            background: #F1E5D6;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #9B6E48;
        }
        .record-details {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #7C5D42;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: 6px;
        }
        .record-details span {
            background: #FBF5EA;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 5px;
        }
        .delete-btn {
            background: #F5E0D0;
            color: #AD6B3C;
            border: none;
            padding: 5px 12px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            width: auto;
            font-weight: 500;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .delete-btn:active {
            background: #EAD0BC;
        }
        .empty-msg {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            color: #BC9A7A;
        }
        .stats {
            background: #FCF6EC;
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #7C5D42;
            border: 1px solid #EDDFC7;
        }
        .install-guide {
            background: #FCF3E6;
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            border-left: 6px solid #D9B48B;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #6E4F34;
        }

        /* 小遊戲專屬樣式 */
        .game-area {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .bubble {
            font-size: 5rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: transform 0.1s ease;
            user-select: none;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 8px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.1));
        }
        .bubble:active {
            transform: scale(0.9);
        }
        .game-score {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #D9B48B;
            background: #FCF6EC;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 24px;
            border-radius: 60px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .game-highscore {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #9B7B5C;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .click-feedback {
            position: fixed;
            pointer-events: none;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #D9B48B;
            text-shadow: 0 0 5px white;
            z-index: 1000;
            animation: floatUp 0.6s ease-out forwards;
        }
        @keyframes floatUp {
            0% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0px) scale(1); }
            100% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-60px) scale(1.2); }
        }
        hr {
            margin: 12px 0;
            border-color: #EADBC5;
        }
        @media (max-width: 550px) {
            .card { padding: 1.2rem; }
            .flex-row { flex-direction: column; gap: 0.7rem; }
            .record-header { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 6px; }
            .bubble { font-size: 4rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <!-- 安裝指引 -->
    <div class="install-guide">
        📲 <strong>安裝到手機桌面</strong> ｜ Safari/Chrome 點分享圖示 → 加入主畫面，即可像 App 使用。<br>
        ✅ 所有資料自動儲存在本機，關閉也不會遺失。🎮 下方還有奶茶小遊戲！
    </div>

    <!-- 主要表單卡片：新增售後服務紀錄 -->
    <div class="card">
        <h1><span>🛠️</span> 售後服務追蹤</h1>
        <div class="sub">記錄客戶購買與服務歷程，提升回購率</div>

        <div class="flex-row">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>📅 服務日期</label>
                <input type="date" id="serviceDate" value="">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>📅 原購買日期</label>
                <input type="date" id="purchaseDate" value="">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex-row">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>🧑‍🦰 客戶姓名</label>
                <input type="text" id="customerName" placeholder="例：陳美華" autocomplete="off">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>📞 聯絡電話 (選填)</label>
                <input type="tel" id="customerPhone" placeholder="手機 / 市話" autocomplete="off">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex-row">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>🏷️ 購買產品</label>
                <input type="text" id="productName" placeholder="例：纖纖飲X / 爆纖錠" list="productList">
                <datalist id="productList">
                    <option>纖纖飲X</option><option>爆纖錠</option><option>纖飄錠</option>
                    <option>纖酵宿</option><option>紫纖飲</option><option>肽纖飲</option>
                    <option>厚奶茶</option><option>洗髮露</option><option>養髮液</option>
             
